content: KDE keeps on giving!Know the little annoying app icon next to minimize button? Well if you press it and go to More Actions -> Configure Window/App Settings you can literally add rules for EVERYTHING imaginable!Like for example, I launch apps in specific workspaces. In combination with the Floating Tile Kwin Script I just press icons and things happen automagically for me. It's insane!I know I just posted about not being an annoying Linux guy, but this is just SOOOO good! XD
